  "accessibility_and_testing": {
    "testIdStrategy": "All interactive elements MUST have a testID property (e.g., testID='y-aller-button')."
  },
  "instructions_to_main_agent": "Implement a React Native Expo app. Follow standard mobile UI/UX principles with native components (SafeAreaView, View, Text, ScrollView, TouchableOpacity). Use React Native StyleSheet API. NO string values for sizes, ONLY integers (e.g. fontSize: 16, not '16px'). All colors MUST be hex format as requested. Build three main flows: Onboarding (3 steps), Map with pulsing markers using react-native-maps, and Bottom Sheet terrace details. Add a timeline slider for sun tracking. For Dark Mode, use React Native's Appearance API or a Theme Provider to switch between the provided light and dark hex palettes."
